title: An Se-bok
text: An Se-bok (born 29 October 1946) is a <a href="North%20Korea">North Korea</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> who played for <a href="North%20Korea%20national%20football%20team">North Korea</a> in the <a href="1966%20FIFA%20World%20Cup">1966 FIFA World Cup</a>. He also played for <a href="Amrokgang%20Sports%20Team">Amrokgang Sports Team</a>.
